# Debug backend service interactions

When investigating cross-service bugs (REST → gRPC → NATS → Realtime WS):

1. Reproduce with `docker compose --profile app up` (or note the failing action).
2. Run **`make compose-logs-collect`** → [`.local/compose.log`](../../.local/compose.log).
3. Search by **`request_id`** (from Flutter `X-Request-Id` or Gateway response header) or by **`chat_id`** / **`message_id`** / **`event_id`**.
4. Follow `event` values in order: `http_access` (gateway) → `grpc_call` (messaging) → `nats_publish` → `nats_consume` (realtime) → `ws_fanout`.

Tier-0 services log JSON to stdout; do not assume Loki/Grafana locally.
